text: George Flynn (born 1937) is an American composer and pianist. George Flynn may also refer to: *George Flynn (baseball) (1871–1901), baseball player *George Flynn (movie producer) on Obsessed *George Flynn (trombonist), jazz trombonist on So Damn Happy etc. and Broadway musician *George J.
